{"tid":318407,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"57歲水吧師傅九成皮膚燒傷　女東主憂心員工安危","createTime":"2017-07-12T05:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T09:21:32.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af142a96f1bfcdf38f9162a0719a9bceed2785d7","tid":318407,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170712/s00001/1336d70db2a12ed66440d35c92b8130a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170712%2Fs00001%2F1336d70db2a12ed66440d35c92b8130a.jpg&h=fa66bb45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土瓜灣長寧街35號地下一間食肆發生氣體爆炸，早上6時許，食肆職員開石油氣爐時發生爆炸，共4人燒傷，其中57歲姓吳水吧師傅身體約九成皮膚燒傷，送院時昏迷，其後再轉送威爾斯親王醫院救治，其妻子事後趕至醫院了解，憂心不已。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，吳與同任飲食業的妻子育有一對子女，他在行內任職多年，兩年前經友人介紹到涉事的茶餐廳工作，任水吧工作，其後離職。約半個月前，女東主再邀請他到店舖工作，日薪約700元。吳為人勤奮及孝順，每周工作6天，下班後即回家煮飯給子女，周日放假則到老人院探望行動不便的母親。<br />\n<br />\n而事件中受驚及受輕傷送院的姓李女店東，意外後仍猶有餘悸。她表示，與胞妹合資經營茶餐廳，開業已十多年。事發時，店內有兩名客人，她正於樓面工作，另一名姓吳水吧師傅則在廚房用電子爐翻熱食物，當吳準備開啟石油氣爐煮牛肉時，突然發生爆炸，她即時逃出店外，受了輕傷，目前十分擔憂伙計的傷勢。李續指，店內有兩個煮食爐，一個是電子爐，另一個是石油氣高速爐，而石油氣爐已於今年初完成檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n李的胞妹事後亦返回現場了解情況，她一度情緒激動，坐在路邊哭泣。"},{"pid":"3fb022ef55b17640140355e6e6b629ecda4d6ed8","tid":318407,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170712/s00001/1499835101504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170712%2Fs00001%2F1499835101504&d=824RU93fzWklzC%2BX%2F3vUCUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=682819ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170712%2Fs00001%2F1499835101504&h=9ea71450\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170712/s00001/1499835101504</a>"},{"pid":"fc5c8fc244f96e1044ce9b2f34fbd50febb34dcf","tid":318407,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好危險，係咪漏氣？"},{"pid":"c0a8d14ddb58b0835c9330f5cb524bc30ed202d5","tid":318407,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:20:37.000Z","msg":"九成皮膚燒傷，相信好難捱得過，祝福佢無事。"},{"pid":"f081c4b2072495eb3f28a9dac0255d47eff4bf5b","tid":318407,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2034a1bdeeb1d2ab3f939d587e6432b226d3eae6","tid":318407,"uid":44898,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:21:13.000Z","msg":"大口同佢2姊妹  接手間野無十幾年<br />\n<br />\n同埋檔野係食夾棍呃番泥<br />\n<br />\n聽到爆炸真係心涼"},{"pid":"692f6b4d8d9267c6008768c2df83de0273406d57","tid":318407,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大口同佢2姊妹  接手間野無十幾年<br />\n<br />\n同埋檔野係食夾棍呃番泥<br />\n<br />\n聽到爆炸真係心涼</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af388d504c91180f9cd686d7216ad0bff8295c59","tid":318407,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大口同佢2姊妹  接手間野無十幾年<br />\n<br />\n同埋檔野係食夾棍呃番泥<br />\n<br />\n聽到爆炸真係心涼</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又有內幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85924070cbff5b3d16e615a9536d8206bcfb5865","tid":318407,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8720828b44629f24a65516446c83c104260022c1","tid":318407,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大口同佢2姊妹  接手間野無十幾年<br />\n<br />\n