Z","msg":"講多樣，新聞影住好味道<br />\n<br />\n左邊紅色門口間密宗佛會<br />\n<br />\n又係倒牌果味野，賺大把錢呀<br />\n一樓成層係佢地<br />\n佛堂老闆揸賓利<br />\n<br />\n大把傻西係到做義工"},{"pid":"2389ee13f047a0842f26f2070cbc4072238871fa","tid":318407,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:37:06.000Z","msg":"東主:佢番唔到工,啲野邊個做? (設計對白)"},{"pid":"37ecef71265d610ca8c73b60bf7a7610f8940621","tid":318407,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋好味道係碰槓地檔<br />\n以前租埋隔離鋪位開檔<br />\n好多人係果到輸光光<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係長寧街都知檔野咩事啦<br />\n我仲以為上凝什人噴油<br />\n今次俾人炸</blockquote><br />\n原來呢個年代仲有低下層咁講野法<br />\n又幾趣緻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇覺得自己好威"},{"pid":"f8251c6b501f31b1e3eb21a60c041030ab84f2c3","tid":318407,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:37:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f7d8c17236731573a30b6de0d595503bee23a85","tid":318407,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977c8165e11de5776b19080f053dc8a9354176a6","tid":318407,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"仲要打日薪工"},{"pid":"fc9fd6eaa5e910c9f98853166cd0fce92e3bb2f3","tid":318407,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e71abc6c8c38bf615ec41c9b7e8c0d30ed885b","tid":318407,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"9成rip 定都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede63da594935f883398fea08334630bc8a16955","tid":318407,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/